node.text:
Our new Miscellaneous Collection!🧸🛋
This collection is a series of fun, beautiful, and incredibly hard household items. Even including our two brand mascots, Hard Willy & Hell The Hound. All pieces made by us, the Hard Jewelry team. It took a little bit more than a year to perfect each piece- and although each piece isn't perfect, it is an accurate representation of the hard jewelry experience. Hard and fun.... Pause.... Resume... I hope you enjoy🖤 

Our Miscellaneous Collection will be releasing on March 26th @ 8 p.m. MTN time🙂🖤

node.text:
I NEED YOUR HELP‼️ ain’t nothing terrible happen , I just have no clue what our homie is tryna say here

I have 7 theories:

1. He fw our jewelry til he realize it has to much power
2. He fw our jewelry to he realize that real eyes, real lies
3. He fw our jewelry til the resellers started reselling it
4. He fw our jewelry til we realized that every customer should get a freebie in their order
5. He fw our jewelry til we relrealize
6. He fw our jewelry til we reorganized our shipping and business structure and became one of the fastest shippers in the game
7. He fw our jewelry til we started realizing that there’s more to jewelry than just drip, but rather the beautiful community that I can build
No memes today... just pain and yearning😞

node.text:
No memes today... Just pain😞... Can we all say a closing prayer for our homie?

Dear lord, I know our homie shouldn’t have littered by throwing his gum out of the window. But would you please find it in your heart to have their jewelry find it’s way back home?...

Even if the jewelry ends up in someone else’s hands... Just return the jewelry back to a owner... It’s probably so scared and sad right now... It’s probably so cold...😞

Please, in Jewelry we trust. Amen.

node.text:
They say nobody’s perfect, but they probably never met a Hard Jewelry supporter🖤... Bro probably wasn’t even passed out, he was probably just saying a prayer for everyone’s safety at Rolling Loud🥺

Maybe he was taking a nap after helping out other people get in front of the concert... 

Here’s to our supporters being the best, cheers 🥂

*clinks glass with you and slams the mimosa in one gulp*
